rComments: Best professor ever! It was clear that he put effort into the lectures and responded quickly to emails and was engaging.

Pretty solid course. I would recommend this course to geography majors and minors. Lectures are reflected in tests fairly. Not the most engaging, but he is there for you for ample support as well as quick to respond to emails. Good and fun assignment, but prepare well for the final exam.
Nice prof! ez course, definitely a good choice for elective credits gg

new professor for this class. Free 10% participation in TUT section.  Mid-term test was fair and most of the parts were selective. You can  simply ignore some parts you don't want to read. All you need to do is study the lecture slides and you r good to go. He responds his email so fast and efficiently, and I found it always helpful to email him.
